# ERC1155标准接口

## 简介
```
erc1155的标准接口
erc1155可以是同质化代币,也可以是非同质化代币,取决已它的一个tokenId发行多少token
```

## 交易接口
#### 1.转账
```JavaScript
    function safeTransferFrom(
        address from,
        address to,
        uint256 id,
        uint256 amount,
        bytes memory data
    ) external;

    入参:
        from: 转出地址
        to: 转入地址
        ids: tokenId
        amounts: token数量
        data: 额外数据,一般没有,可以传入0x
```

#### 2.批量转账
```JavaScript
    function safeBatchTransferFrom(
        address from,
        address to,
        uint256[] memory ids,
        uint256[] memory amounts,
        bytes memory data
    ) external;
    说明: `memory`是关键字,不影响入参

    入参: 
        from: 转出地址
        to: 转入地址
        ids: tokenId, 数组, 与amounts的下标对应
        amounts: token数量, 数组, 与ids的下标对应
        data: 额外数据,一般没有,可以传入0x
```

#### 3.授权/取消授权
```JavaScript
    function setApprovalForAll(address operator, bool approved) external;

    入参:
        operator: 授权目标地址
        approved: 是否授权
```

## 查询接口
#### 1.查询名称
```JavaScript
    function name() external view returns(string memory);

    返回:
        1. string: 全称
```

#### 2.查询简称/代号
```JavaScript
    function symbol() external view returns(string memory);

    返回:
        1. string: 简称
```

#### 3.查询现有铸造量
```JavaScript
    function totalSupply(uint256 id) external view returns(uint256);

    入参:
        id: tokenId
    返回:
        1. uint256: 现有铸造量
```

#### 4.查询元数据uri
```JavaScript
    function uri(uint256 tokenId) external view returns (string memory);

    入参:
        id: tokenId
    返回: 
        1. string: 元数据uri
```

#### 5.查询余额
```JavaScript
    function balanceOf(address account, uint256 id) external view returns (uint256);

    入参:
        account: 要查询的钱包地址
        id: 要查询的tokenId
    返回:
        1. uint256: 余额
```

#### 6.批量查询余额
```JavaScript
    function balanceOfBatch(address[] memory accounts, uint256[] memory ids)external view returns(uint256[] memory);
    说明: `memory`是关键字,不影响入参

    入参: 
        accounts: 要查询的钱包地址, 数组, 与ids下标对应
        ids: 要查询的tokenId, 数组, 与accounts下标对应
    返回:
        1. uint256: 余额, 数组
```

#### 7.是否已授权
```JavaScript
    function isApprovedForAll(address account, address operator) external view returns (bool);

    入参:
        account: token持有地址
        operator: 授权目标
    返回:
        1. bool: account是否将token全部授权给operator
```
